Hello! I'm Zach and my goal is to provide the best possible rental experience for every guest. If you have any questions about my vehicles, please email dciautosct@gmail.com.

I have an excellent selection of luxury, sport and economy cars available.

I offer co-hosting and fleet management for other Turo hosts. Vehicle storage, cleaning, guest communication and more to keep your business running 24/7.
Hello I'm Dylan! I'm passionate in providing you with a great and enjoyable experience on Turo! I take pride in offering the cleanest vehicles. My service of excellence will not let you down!
I was an uber driver for 7 years before my wife and I started our car rental company in 2022. I love to provide great cars for great prices with great customer service.
I am a commercial truck driver. I travel alot. Dream car is a 1968 VW Microbus which I someday hope to restore.

Hi all/Hola a todos! I am Kiara Cruz and I am a young-adult entrepreneur with an unwavering passion for cars, particularly the feel of driving nice ones. My travels have taken me to some incredible places, with the Dominican Republic, Colombia, and Mexico holding a special place in my heart. These destinations have gifted me unforgettable memories and a deep appreciation for diverse cultures.

Speaking of cars, my dream ride is the Mercedes EQS, a testament to the future of automotive innovation that one day I hope to own. Anyways, I've been navigating the roads since I was 16, starting in beautiful Puerto Rico with my trusty Nissan Rogue a car that taught me that safety and responsibility are forefront to being behind the wheel.

When I'm not chasing adventures or exploring new horizons, I can be found doing Pilates to stay fit and healthy or winding down by catching up on TV shows but the moments  I cherish the most are spent with family and friends as they are the true treasures in life.

In essence, my love for cars is matched by my commitment to responsible driving and respect for the vehicles I use and lend. 

I'm thrilled to be a part of this community and look forward to sharing new experiences and memories with you!
